Module com.example.projectc482
Package com.example.projectc482.controller

Class MainController

java.lang.Object
com.example.projectc482.controller.MainController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This is the Main hub for the GUI and acts as the intermediary for the rest of the windows. This class is what is used to display the main window and also holds the methods for opening all other windows.
